description:
Keith is Sam’s little brother.
Sam had done his video with us and had gone home, and hadn’t intended on telling his brother anything about it.
But, you know how little brothers can be, and Sam eventually broke down and told him.
“No way! I want to do it!” was how Keith told us he responded.
Keith had turned 18 several months before we had met Sam. I was a little hesitant when I found out that Keith was still in high school.
“I’m a senior,” he told us. “My birthday was right on the edge, so I started school later than other kids my age.”
Keith is looking forward to graduating so he can go to college.
“I want to be a pilot,” he told us.
Another interesting bit of information he offered is that he’s a virgin.
“Yep, this gentleman is still a virgin,” he said with a big smile.
title: Keith
